==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: telemarketing
<hw>telemarketing</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the use of the telephone as an
interactive medium for promotion; calling potential customers by
telephone for the purpose of selling something; -- applied especially to
calls made to persons who have not previously contacted the
seller.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> teleselling.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Telemechanic</ent>⟦br⟧
